2026-05-10T04:08:30.4012713Z 21    <!--
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4013128Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4013341Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4013717Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4014081Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4014454Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T04:08:30.4014809Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
